==Text==
''The words of wisdom left here by the Lord Ravager known as "Celenova":''

<div align="center">From across the void of space and time, I witnessed a single soul embark on a cosmic journey.<br />
And in that instant, a billion clocks began to turn.<br />
If the doom of the cosmos does not arrive with the birth of Irontomb, it will be...<br />
in that moment when the stars will scatter like frightened birds,<br />
and all that is harmony and discord, perfect and incomplete, just fall into oblivion.</div>

